title: 4 ROOM 1 BEDROOM Garden Apt.
posting_body: ['4 Room, 1 Bedroom NEWLY REMODELED Garden Apartment in JEFFERSON PARK-Near Milwaukee and Agatite.', 'Very Close to Public Transportation (Buses and Trains)', '; Close to Expressways, Plenty of Parking, Laundry Facilities on Site, Air Conditioner Wall Unit, Storage Area.', 'A Very Clean and Secure Apartment and Building.', 'Newer Appliances and Carpeting.', '$795.00 + Security Deposit.', 'Utilities (Gas/Electric) Separate.', 'Background Check; Credit Check.', 'No Pets/No Smokers.', 'Available:  July 01.', 'Email or Call 773/777-0440 (If not home or available to answer the call, please leave name, number, and best time to call).', "Room Dimensions: Bedroom 12' x 13' (w/ Closet) Carpeted; Front Room 9.5' x 12'; Vestibule 9' x 8' (w/ Closet and Linen Closet); Kitchen 9' x 13'; Small Office 9' x 10' (w/ Closet) Carpeted; Bathroom 5' x 8'.", 'Apartment Total Square Footage: 600 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Photos of:  Kitchen, Vestibule, Bathroom, Front Room, Bedroom, Bedroom Closet, Office, Office Closet.']
